SUMMARY:Easter and Spring Mini Portraits
DESCRIPTION:Easter and Spring Mini Portraits with Village Studio at Lorrimer Sanctuary.\nSaturday April 4th\, 9am -12pm \nWe are excited to announce our Easter + Spring Mini Sessions at Lorrimer Sanctuary in Franklin Lakes\, NJ on Saturday\, April 4th\, where we will have a floral stand decorated for the perfect backdrop to Spring and Easter Portraits for your little ones. Always a time of hope\, spring reminds us of rebirth and new beginnings. 20% of the proceeds of this event will be donated to Lorrimer Sanctuary. \nTickets are required and you can purchase online \nBUY TICKETS
